<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/143003011/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Evaluation is based in two projects: the analysis of an unsteady flow by linear potential methods (either incompressible, subsonic or supersonic) and the analysis of an steady flow. The project is done in groups of four and the presentation done by one of the group members.
A final exam is also possible for those that not follow the project evaluation."""@es ;
    ns1:hasEvaluationTrial <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/143003011/2025-26/evaluation/trial1>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/143003011/2025-26/evaluation/trial2> .

